  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.282154726368428         -7.6778          -177.05          -740.80
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.078389924487961          2.1331            49.19           205.81
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.043391318169458         -1.1807           -27.23          -113.92
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.259541459295110          7.0625           162.86           681.43
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

